comments: Aldridge (BKN) firms up in a screening position in the path of Grimes (NYK) and does not deliver contact.
Grimes (NYK) legally contests Thomas' (BKN) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.

As Randle (NYK) hands the ball off, he turns towards the basket and briefly engages with Thomas (BKN) as he goes underneath the pick.
